ew capital are collectively the single largest investor in the fund referencesedit  sageview capital  about us  history sageview capital retrieved october     kkrs two rising stars depart to launch fund pdf the wall street journal september     kkr loses leadership candidates pdf financial times september     kkr financial makes cash king forbes august   external linksedit sageview capital company website this article about a financial services corporation of the united states is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlesageviewcapitaloldid categories united states financial services company stubsinvestment management companies of the united stateshidden categories pages using deprecated image syntaxall stub articles navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages add links this page was last edited on  january  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundation inc a nonprofit organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view sasank chary sageview capital lp profile  biography  bloomberg feedback sasank chary partner sageview capital lp career history partner sageview capital lp present principal sageview capital lp  associate harvest partners inc unknown analyst ubs securities llc former show 